  "text": "In this short paper we focus on the setting of finite horizon MDPs. By comparison, previous optimistic approaches to exploration, such as UCRL2, provide bounds for the more general setting of weakly communicating MDPs [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] ). However, we believe that much of the insight from the UCBVI algorithm (and its analysis) will carry over to this more general setting using existing techniques such as 'the doubling trick' [CITATION_3] .",
